@NODE #fcoment "File comment support"
	@{B}File Comment support
	--------------------@{UB}

	You can choose what file comment should be
	added to file or none.

	- do not change
		dont touch file comment

	- based on image info
		file comment created from image info
		e.g. ILBM - 00320 x 00512 - 256

	- user`s specified text
		you can enter your own file comment
		in string gadget below

	- clean up
		clean up file comment if any exists
		(from target file not source)

@ENDNODE
@NODE #url "URL detection"
	@{B}URL Detection
	-------------@{UB}

	The program has built-in URL detection.

	If URL exists in image description it will be 
	placed in listview on Note page.

	Just double-click one of them and the program
	will call OpenURL library and then your Web Browser
	will be launched.

	Please refer to OpenURL docs for information how
	to select which Web Browser and/or e-mail client
	should be launched.

	Since v2.4 FTP links are also detected.

@ENDNODE
